  h2 Attention
  p The International Journal of Creative Research & Publications (IJCRP) invites researchers, academicians, scholars, and professionals to submit their valuable contributions for its upcoming issues. The journal welcomes 
    strong original research articles, review papers, conceptual studies, and innovative scholarly works
    | from all disciplines, reflecting its truly multidisciplinary scope.
  p IJCRP provides a global platform to showcase high-quality research that addresses contemporary academic, professional, and societal challenges. By publishing with IJCRP, authors gain international visibility, rigorous peer review, and wide dissemination of their work.
  p In addition, IJCRP is inviting 
    strong qualified and dedicated academicians
    | to join its Editorial Board. Editorial members will play a vital role in maintaining academic standards, guiding the peer-review process, and shaping the future of multidisciplinary research.
  strong 📌 Submit your manuscript or apply to be an editor today and contribute meaningfully to the advancement of global scholarship.

  h3 Focus & Scope of the Journal

  p The International Journal of Creative Research & Publications (IJCRP) publishes high-quality original research articles, review papers, short communications, and conceptual studies across a wide range of academic disciplines. The journal is committed to promoting creative, innovative, and interdisciplinary research that contributes to the advancement of knowledge and addresses contemporary academic, professional, and societal challenges.
  
  p IJCRP provides an inclusive scholarly platform for researchers to present their original ideas, experimental findings, theoretical frameworks, and practical applications. The journal encourages comprehensive and methodologically sound research with sufficient detail to ensure transparency, reproducibility, and academic rigor. There is no restriction on manuscript length, provided the content is scientifically sound, original, and well-structured.

  p The primary aim of IJCRP is to facilitate the exchange of innovative research and intellectual perspectives among scholars from diverse disciplines, thereby strengthening interdisciplinary collaboration and global academic engagement.

